ygData.messageBody:
Lvl 12? Man, I was lvl 40 and getting killed by those frickin' little
brownies. One day I will have my revenge. You also have Equestrielle the
Corrupt (a high lvl necromancer unicorn). Biyatch harmtouched me for like
500dmg. Then there's the inky camp. I think there's a brownie camp. A faerie
camp. Orc camps.. shadow men camp.. Nybright sister's bandit camp...
luv,
-Su

> Lol, I understand your frustration! Tonight I ventured hunting in Lesser
> Fey with my lvl12 WE Ranger, Well needless to say it was a little more
> than what I was expecting! I figured by at least 12, I can very well
> hold my own over there! NOT!
>
